# Artificial Intelligence

Artificial Intelligence (AI) is one of the most transformative technologies of the modern era. It enables machines to perform tasks that typically require human intelligence, such as learning, reasoning, and decision-making.

AI is widely used in healthcare, education, finance, transportation, and many other industries. It helps improve efficiency, reduce human effort, and provide better solutions to complex problems.

As technology continues to evolve, AI is expected to play an even greater role in shaping the future and creating new opportunities for innovation and growth.
